text: The 2020 United States presidential election in Kentucky was held on Tuesday, November 3, 2020, as part of the 2020 United States presidential election. Incumbent President Donald Trump and running mate Vice President Mike PenceKentucky had won 8 electoral votes in the Electoral College. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election Category:2020s in Kentucky
title: 2020 United States presidential election in Kentucky
